messages.message:
Hey team! I just merged the PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/58683). From now on, all PR that runs Cypress will create a community user, a commercial org admin, a commercial org user, and one new commercial org. For now, all tests by default will still use the pre-existing users and orgs. I'll put up another PR to change the default to use the new users and add overrides for tests that depend on existing users.
Example usage:
```    cy.login({
      xhr: true,
      user: CyUser.COMMERCIAL_AIHUB_DEFAULT,
      usePreExistingUser: true | false
    });```
Please override all aihub-results tests in flow-review and review-reviewer-dashboard + review-manager-dashboard so they use the existing config
